\c 40
\s Ukumiswa kwethabhanekele lokungcweliswa kwalo
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Ngosuku lwenyanga yokuqala\x + 12.2; 13.4.\x*, ngolokuqala lwenyanga, uzamisa ithabhanekele, ithente lenhlangano\x + 40.17; 26.1-30.\x*,
\v 3 ubusufaka lapho umtshokotsho wobufakazi, umbomboze umtshokotsho ngeveyili\x + 40.21; 35.12.\x*.
\v 4 Ungenise itafula\x + 40.22; 26.35.\x*, uhlele okuhlelwayo phezu kwalo; ungenise uluthi lwesibane, ulumathise izibane zalo\x + 40.24,25.\x*.
\v 5 Ubeke ilathi legolide lempepha phambi komtshokotsho wobufakazi\x + 40.26; 39.38.\x*, ulengise isilenge somnyango wethabhanekele.
\v 6 Ubeke ilathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa phambi komnyango wethabhanekele wethente lenhlangano\x + 40.29.\x*,
\v 7 ubeke inditshi yokugezela phakathi kwethente lenhlangano lelathi\x + 40.30; 30.18.\x*, uthele amanzi lapho.
\v 8 Umise iguma inhlangothi zonke, ulengise isilenge sesango leguma.
\v 9 Uthathe amafutha okugcoba, ugcobe ithabhanekele lakho konke okukulo\x + 30.26.\x*, ulingcwelise lempahla yalo yonke, njalo lizakuba ngcwele.
\v 10 Njalo ugcobe ilathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 30.28.\x* lezitsha zalo zonke, ulingcwelise ilathi, njalo ilathi lizakuba yingcwelengcwele.
\v 11 Njalo ugcobe inditshi yokugezela lonyawo lwayo\x + 30.28.\x*, uyingcwelise.
\v 12 Usondeze uAroni lamadodana akhe emnyango wethente lenhlangano\x + Levi 8.1-13.\x*, ubagezise ngamanzi.
\v 13 Ugqokise uAroni izembatho ezingcwele, umgcobe, umngcwelise, ukuze angisebenzele njengompristi\x + 28.41.\x*.
\v 14 Usondeze amadodana akhe, uwagqokise izigqoko,
\v 15 uwagcobe njengalokhu ugcobe uyise, ukuze angisebenzele njengabapristi; kuzakuthi-ke ukugcotshwa kwabo kuzakuba kubo yibupristi obuphakade kuzizukulwana zabo\x + Nani 25.13.\x*.
\v 16 UMozisi wenza njengakho konke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayimlaye khona; wenza njalo.
\p
\v 17 Kwasekusithi ngenyanga yokuqala ngomnyaka wesibili ngolokuqala lwenyanga ithabhanekele lamiswa\x + 40.1,2. Nani 7.1.\x*.
\v 18 UMozisi wasemisa ithabhanekele; wabeka phansi izisekelo zalo, wamisa amapulanka alo, wafaka imithando yalo, wamisa insika zalo.
\v 19 Wendlala ithente phezu kwethabhanekele, wabeka isifulelo sethente phezu kwalo phezulu, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi.
\p
\v 20 Wathatha wafaka ubufakazi emtshokotshweni, wafaka imijabo emtshokotshweni, wafaka isihlalo somusa ngaphezu komtshokotsho phezulu\x + 25.16; 16.34.\x*.
\v 21 Wangenisa umtshokotsho ethabhanekeleni, wamisa iveyili lesembeso wambomboza umtshokotsho wobufakazi\x + 40.3; 35.12.\x*, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi.
\p
\v 22 Wasefaka itafula ethenteni lenhlangano\x + 40.4; 26.35.\x*, eceleni kwethabhanekele ngenyakatho ngaphandle kweveyili,
\v 23 wahlela isinkwa ngohlelo phezu kwalo phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 40.4.\x*\nd*, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi.
\p
\v 24 Wafaka uluthi lwesibane ethenteni lenhlangano\x + 26.35.\x*, maqondana letafula, eceleni kwethabhanekele ngeningizimu.
\v 25 Walumathisa izibane phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 40.4; 25.37.\x*\nd*, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi.
\p
\v 26 Wafaka ilathi legolide ethenteni lenhlangano phambi kweveyili\x + 40.5; 30.6.\x*,
\v 27 watshisa kulo impepha elephunga elimnandi\x + 30.7.\x*, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi.
\p
\v 28 Walengisa isilenge somnyango wethabhanekele\x + 40.5; 26.36.\x*.
\v 29 Wabeka ilathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa emnyango wethabhanekele lethente lenhlangano\x + 40.6.\x*, wanikela kulo umnikelo wokutshiswa lomnikelo wokudla\x + 29.41; 30.9.\x*, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi.
\p
\v 30 Wabeka inditshi yokugezela phakathi kwethente lenhlangano lelathi\x + 40.7.\x*, wathela lapho amanzi okugeza.
\v 31 UMozisi loAroni lamadodana akhe bagezela kuyo izandla zabo lenyawo zabo;
\v 32 ekungeneni kwabo ethenteni lenhlangano lekusondeleni kwabo elathini bageza, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi\x + 30.19-21.\x*.
\v 33 Wasemisa iguma lazingelezela ithabhanekele lelathi\x + 40.8; 27.9,16.\x*, walengisa isilenge sesango leguma. UMozisi wasewuqeda umsebenzi.
\s Iyezi laliphezu kwethabhanekele
\p
\v 34 Iyezi laselisibekela ithente lenhlangano\x + 13.21.\x*, lenkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yagcwalisa ithabhanekele\x + 29.43. Levi 16.2. Nani 9.15. 1 Kho. 8.10,11. 2 Lan. 5.13,14; 7.2. Isa. 6.4. Hag. 2.7,9. Isam. 15.8.\x*.
\v 35 Ngakho uMozisi wayengelakungena ethenteni lenhlangano, ngoba iyezi lahlala phezu kwalo lenkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yagcwalisa ithabhanekele\x + 29.43. Levi 16.2. Nani 9.15. 1 Kho. 8.10,11. 2 Lan. 5.13,14; 7.2. Isa. 6.4. Hag. 2.7,9. Isam. 15.8.\x*.
\v 36 Lalapho iyezi lisenyuswa lisuka ethabhanekeleni, abantwana bakoIsrayeli baqhubekela phambili enhambeni zabo zonke\x + Nani 9.17. 10.11. Neh. 9.19.\x*,
\v 37 kodwa lapho iyezi lingenyuswanga kabahambanga kuze kufike usuku lokwenyuswa kwalo\x + Nani 9.19-22.\x*.
\v 38 Ngoba iyezi leN\nd kosi\nd* laliphezu kwethabhanekele emini, lomlilo wawuphezu kwalo ebusuku, phambi kwamehlo endlu yonke yakoIsrayeli, enhambeni zabo zonke.